      <Content m="2015-10-28T03:43:48.293959Z">&lt;P&gt;You can resize the column width at run time. By default property &lt;STRONG&gt;allowColumnResize&lt;/STRONG&gt; is set as "&lt;STRONG&gt;True&lt;/STRONG&gt;".&lt;/P&gt;&lt;innovasys:widget type="Note Box" layout="block"&gt;&lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="block" name="Content"&gt;Spread.Views does not support&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;"zero"&lt;/STRONG&gt; width.&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt; &lt;/innovasys:widget&gt;
&lt;P&gt;To allow resize of column, use&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;allowColumnResize&lt;/STRONG&gt; property:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;innovasys:widget type="Colorized Example Code" layout="block"&gt;&lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="inline" name="Title"&gt;JavaScript&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt; &lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="inline" name="LanguageName"&gt;JS&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt; &lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="block" name="Content"&gt;allowColumnResize: true&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt; &lt;/innovasys:widget&gt;</Content>
